---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TopBanner from '../../components/TopBanner.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import PageHeader from '../../components/PageHeader.astro';
import CTABanner from '../../components/CTABanner.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import heroImage from '../../assets/images/hero-image.jpg';
import WorkingCommittee from '../../components/WorkingCommittee.astro';
---

<Layout title="Finland - FiNAN">
  <main>
    <TopBanner />
    <Navbar />
    <PageHeader
      title="Finland"
      description="Discover healthcare opportunities in Finland, the land of a thousand lakes, known for innovation, education excellence, and comprehensive healthcare."
      backgroundImage={heroImage}
      backgroundAlt="Finnish forest and lakes landscape"
    />

    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">
            Healthcare in Finland
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Finland offers exceptional opportunities for Filipino healthcare professionals in a country renowned for its world-class education system, technological innovation, and comprehensive healthcare coverage. Known as the "Land of a Thousand Lakes," Finland combines cutting-edge medical technology with a strong commitment to patient care and professional development.
          </p>

          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            The Finnish healthcare system is built on the principles of equality, accessibility, and quality care for all residents. Healthcare professionals benefit from excellent working conditions, competitive compensation, and extensive opportunities for continuing education and specialization.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Healthcare System Excellence
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Finland's healthcare system combines public and private sectors effectively, with municipalities responsible for organizing healthcare services. The country is known for its innovative digital health solutions, research excellence, and emphasis on preventive care, providing healthcare professionals with opportunities to work with the latest medical technologies and evidence-based practices.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Finnish Culture and Lifestyle
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Finland offers a unique Nordic lifestyle characterized by a close connection to nature, seasonal celebrations, and the concept of "sisu" - determination and resilience. The country provides excellent work-life balance, with extensive parental leave policies, outdoor recreation opportunities, and a strong social support system that values international professionals.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Professional Development
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Finnish healthcare emphasizes continuous learning and professional growth. Healthcare professionals have access to world-class training programs, research opportunities, and international collaboration. The country's commitment to innovation in healthcare technology provides exciting opportunities for career advancement and specialization.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <WorkingCommittee country="finland" />
    <CTABanner />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
